QorIQ Yocto SDK Project
=============================

To get the SDK you need to have `repo` installed and use it as:

Install the `repo` utility:
$: mkdir ~/bin
$: curl https://storage.googleapis.com/git-repo-downloads/repo > ~/bin/repo
$: chmod a+x ~/bin/repo

Download the SDK source:
$: export PATH=${PATH}:~/bin
$: mkdir yocto-sdk
$: cd yocto-sdk
$: repo init -u https://github.com/qoriq-open-source/yocto-sdk.git -b master
$: repo sync --no-clone-bundle

Start build (ls1088ardb as an example):
$: . ./setup-env -m ls1088ardb
